nodes.text: Squad Three-Zero-One was a Jedi TwinTail starfighter unit composed of the Jedi Te Corso, Asaak Dan, Drok, and Sayar Dun'La, who met up with Admiral Gar Stazi to discuss the possibility of the New Jedi Order aiding the joined Anti-Sith treaty of the Galactic Alliance Remnant and Empire-in-exile in 137 ABY.
